      "text": "After Bitcoin came altcoins ([[Namecoin]] in 2011), various [[Forks of Bitcoin]], and so-called second generation ([[Ethereum]]) then [[Third Generation Blockchains]] (listed in no order: [[Cardano]], [[Tezos]], [[Holochain]] and [[EOS]], for instance). These reflected different schools of thought about the computer-science underpinning system features and performance. The very sustainability and direction of such ongoing technical development is reflected in more philosophical and political lines of inquiry such as experimenting with various models of governance."
